abstract: Pentagon says Adan Garar, senior member of Shabab militant group, was killed in drone strike in Somalia.
lead_paragraph: The Defense Department said that Adan Garar, a senior member of the Shabab extremist group, had been killed in a drone strike on his vehicle last week.

headline.main: Pentagon Confirms Strike Killed Shabab Militant Leader in Somalia
headline.print_headline: Somali Militant Is Killed in Strike
